\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Terminal weak-pi pODMR resonance refinement. The refined center is close to the broad strong-pi center, ruling out a large electron-resonance mis-centering explanation for the earlier Ramsey high-frequency component.}}{4}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
